	<aboutCourseTitle><![CDATA[Introduction]]></aboutCourseTitle>
	<aboutCourseContent><![CDATA[Performance management is about how you help your life insurance professionals develop and become more successful as individuals and as a team. However, before you can do either of these, you need to make sure that your team members know what they need to achieve and that they are motivated enough to do it.<br>

After you have completed this module, you should be able to:<br>
• Define performance management and understand where it fits within the sales management process<br>
• Explain the key areas within the performance management process<br>
• Explain the importance of performance planning and measurement<br>]]>
	</aboutCourseContent>
	
